[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]Health and safety is an important part o
[normal]f any industry, particularly in the offshore 
[normal]oil and gas 
[normal]sector, which is classe
[normal]d as a major hazards industry.
