[normal]ith the International Oil &amp; Gas Producers Association (OGP) Aviation Safety Committee’s (ASC) worldwide fatal and non-fatal reportable accident rates for the period 1995 to 2010 the data indicates that, averaged over this time, offshore helicopter operatio
[normal]ns on the UKCS carry significantly less risk than operations elsewhere in the world.
